title: The Quarterly Review of Biology

contents.note: JSTOR (full text also available for subscription or payment)

additional-note: The March 1966 issue (volume 41, number 1) is the first for which a renewal was filed.  Issues with a copyright date of 1964 or later also had their copyrights automatically renewed. The March 1964 issue was the first one so copyrighted. (Copyright notices appeared on the cover of 1964 issues, and might not be visible on digitized versions that omit the covers.)
acknowledgement: Thanks to Kristina Eden Hall for copyright research on this title.
